ss=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Capsicum\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial;\">Capsicum</a></i><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;семейства&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9F%D0%B0%D1%81%D0%BB%D1%91%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%B2%D1%8B%D0%B5\" title=\"Паслёновые\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Паслёновые</a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;(</span><i style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Solanaceae</i><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">), или его плоды.&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A1%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8C%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%BE%D1%85%D0%BE%D0%B7%D1%8F%D0%B9%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B2%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%8F_%D0%BA%D1%83%D0%BB%D1%8C%D1%82%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B0\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Сельскохозяйственная культура\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Сельскохозяйственная</a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9E%D0%B2%D0%BE%D1%89%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%8F_%D0%BA%D1%83%D0%BB%D1%8C%D1%82%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B0\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Овощная культура\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">овощная культура</a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">. Сорта перца стручкового делят на сладкие и горькие. Последним, известным как&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9A%D1%80%D0%B0%D1%81%D0%BD%D1%8B%D0%B9_%D0%BF%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D1%86\" title=\"Красный перец\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">красный перец</a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">, острый вкус придаёт&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%90%D0%BB%D0%BA%D0%B0%D0%BB%D0%BE%D0%B8%D0%B4%D1%8B\" title=\"Алкалоиды\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">алкалоид</a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9A%D0%B0%D0%BF%D1%81%D0%B0%D0%B8%D1%86%D0%B8%D0%BD\" title=\"Капсаицин\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">капсаицин</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-.D0.91.D0.A1.D0.AD_3-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1em; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D1%86_%D1%81%D1%82%D1%80%D1%83%D1%87%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2%D1%8B%D0%B9#cite_note-.D0.91.D0.A1.D0.AD-3\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial;\">[3]</a></sup><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">. Разновидности с плодами сладкого вкуса&nbsp;—&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">пе́рец сла́дкий</b><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">. Существует множество&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A1%D0%BE%D1%80%D1%82\" title=\"Сорт\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">сортотипов</a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">, например,&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">пе́рец болга́рский</b><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">.</span><br></p>',100,1,1,''),(6,'Pepper green','Կանաչ պղպեղ','Перец зеленый','<p><b style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">paprika</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-.D0.A8.D1.80.D0.B5.D1.82.D0.B5.D1.80144_2-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1em; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2 px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D1%86_%D1%81%D1%82%D1%80%D1%83%D1%87%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2%D1%8B%D0%B9#cite_note-.D0.A8.D1.80.D0.B5.D1.82.D0.B5.D1.80144-2\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial;\">[2]</a></sup><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;(</span><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9B%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B8%D0%BD%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B8%D0%B9_%D1%8F%D0%B7%D1%8B%D0%BA\" title=\"Latin language\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">lat.</a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><i style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span lang=\"la\" xml:lang=\"la\">Cápsicum ánnuum</span></i><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">)&nbsp;—&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%91%D0%B8%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%BE%D0%B3%D0%B8%D1%87%D0%B5%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%B8%D0%B9_%D0%B2%D0%B8%D0%B4\" title=\"species\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"></a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;annual&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A2%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B2%D1%8F%D0%BD%D0%B8%D1%81%D1%82%D1%8B%D0%B5_%D1%80%D0%B0%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D1%8F\" title=\"Herbaceous plants\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">herbaceous plants</a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;kind&nbsp;</span><i style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/Capsicum\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Capsicum\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial;\">Capsicum</a></i><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;family&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9F%D0%B0%D1%81%D0%BB%D1%91%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%B2%D1%8B%D0%B5\" title=\"Nightshades\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Solanaceae</a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;(</span><i style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Solanaceae</i><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">), or its fruit.&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A1%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8C%D1%81%D0%BA%D0%BE%D1%85%D0%BE%D0%B7%D1%8F%D0%B9%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B2%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%BD%D0%B0%D1%8F_%D0%BA%D1%83%D0%B