">capsaicin</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-.D0.91.D0.A1.D0.AD_3-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1em; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2 px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D1%86_%D1%81%D1%82%D1%80%D1%83%D1%87%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2%D1%8B%D0%B9#cite_note-.D0.91.D0.A1.D0.AD-3\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial;\">[3]</a></sup><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">. Varieties with fruits of sweet taste&nbsp;—&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">sweet pepper</b><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">. There are many&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%A1%D0%BE%D1%80%D1%82\" title=\"Grade\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">types</a><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"> like&nbsp;</span><b style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">bell peppers</b><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">.</span><br></p>','<p><b style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">պատիճավոր Պղպեղ</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-ը:D0.A8.D1.80.D0.B5.D1.82.D0.B5.D1.80144_2-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"line-height: 1em; unicode-bidi: isolate; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 11.2 px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D1%86_%D1%81%D1%82%D1%80%D1%83%D1%87%D0%BA%D0%BE%D0%B2%D1%8B%D0%B9#cite_note-.D0.A8.D1.80.D0.B5.D1.82.D0.B5.D1.80144-2\" style=\"color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-position: initial;\">[2]</a></s